             was indicted for <rs id="t18300415-256-off1422" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300415-256-off1422" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-256-off1422" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300415-256-cd1423" type="crimeDate">2nd of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-256-off1422 t18300415-256-cd1423"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 4s.; 1 waistcoat, value 10s.; 1 pair of drawers, value 2s. 6d.; 1 pair of stockings, value 1s. 6d. and 1 pair of braces, value 6d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-256-victim2229" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Plant
                        <interp inst="t18300415-256-victim2229" type="surname" value="Plant"></interp>
